{"tid":2076914,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"會然 拾狗帶落山入一入黎","createTime":"2020-06-24T01:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T09:55:16.000Z","uid":73381,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ee85fc388715b69ed800727db27328c63fc51c","tid":2076914,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"［平反］正式宣布足球正名為「玩具」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ayELtpV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ayELtpV</a><br />\n#93 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n搵到point去駁我未呀屌你老母臭閪玩具撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時真係唔怪得人哋笑鳩班玩具撚 你條撚樣完美示範玩具撚係幾咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a106404ec0e9268d54c32a7ce108ade63943d86","tid":2076914,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym6E9zp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym6E9zp.png&h=24f51d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連份report係點評分都唔知就以為執到寶咁打哂飛機<br />\n<br />\n你份垃圾報告就係連你口中嘅運動員都有份去評分呀戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7532bb2218824331301275ad7fe2799b0884c3","tid":2076914,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:58:20.000Z","msg"